ğŸ§  Breast Cancer Prediction using Machine Learning

This project demonstrates a machine learning pipeline for predicting breast cancer (malignant or benign) using the Breast Cancer Wisconsin (Diagnostic) Dataset. The goal is to compare multiple ML models and evaluate their performance in classifying tumors based on various medical features.

